rts several music services like Spotify, YouTube Music, and Apple Music. Once linked via the Google Home app, you can stream music with voice commands or Bluetooth.<\/p>\n<p>To use Bluetooth, say: \u201cHey Google, Bluetooth pairing,\u201d then connect via your phone\u2019s Bluetooth settings.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Controlling Smart Home Devices<\/h2>\n<p>You can control compatible devices such as lights, thermostats, and plugs using your voice. Just say:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u201cHey Google, turn off the living room lights.\u201d<\/li>\n<li>\u201cHey Google, set the thermostat to 22 degrees.\u201d<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Setup for smart home devices is done through the Google Home app.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Making Hands-Free Calls<\/h2>\n<p>In supported regions, you can use your Mini to make voice calls. Just say, \u201cHey Google, call Mom.\u201d Contacts must be synced via the app, and calling features may depend on your country or carrier.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Personal Routines and Reminders<\/h2>\n<p>Create routines that automate tasks. For example, \u201cGood Morning\u201d can trigger a weather report, turn on lights, and play news updates. You can also set reminders and calendar events easily.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Fun and Entertainment<\/h2>\n<p>Ask your Google Home Mini to tell jokes, play trivia games, or make animal sounds \u2014 great for kids and adults alike.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Learn More About Smart Speakers<\/h2>\n<p>To understand how these devices work and compare brands, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Smart_speaker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Smart Speaker on Wikipedia<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2>\u00a0Conclusion<\/h2>\n<p>Learning how to use your Google Home Mini speaker opens a world of convenience. Whether it's streaming music, getting news, or managing your home, this little device can do a lot more than you think.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>How to Use Google Home Mini Speaker? Just connected your de